description: Dialogue Health Technologies Inc. operates a digital healthcare and wellness platform in Canada Germany, and Australia. Its Integrated Health Platform is a healthcare hub that centralizes its programs in a single user-friendly application, which provide access to psychologists, psychotherapists, social workers, physicians, nurses, and health specialists. The company's platform also enables its members and their dependents to access employee assistance, and occupational health and safety programs. It serves employers and organizations. Dialogue Technologies Inc. was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.
